Q2. Given are some following variables containing data: (i) var1 = ‘ ‘ (ii) var2 = ‘[ DS , ML , Python]’ (iii) var3 = [ ‘DS’ , ’ML’ , ‘Python’ ] (iv) var4 = 1. What will be the data type of the above given variable.
In [2]:
var1 = ""
var2 = "[ DS , ML , Python]"
var3 = [ 'D' , 'ML' , 'Python' ]
var4 = 1
print(type(var1))
print(type(var2))
print(type(var3))
print(type(var4))
<class 'str'>
<class 'str'>
<class 'list'>
<class 'int'>

